markdownRemark.rawMarkdownBody:
### So Much to Share, Not Much to Say

'have you seen this new tiktok dance?' </br>
             "Hey, how are you? What's happening in your life? Is all okay?" </br>
'no, what is it?' </br>
             "I don't know, I'm feeling lost.. as if I'm divulging in detrimental behavior" </br>
'isn't it great? wanna make a video in response?' </br>
             "I'm here to listen. Just tell me, whats up?" </br>
'nah man, just don't feel like it' </br>
             "Another time" </br>
'kk, no worries, I'll share it with you, learn the dance and we'll do it next time' </br>
             "Another time then.." </br>
